<section>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-9">
                    <h1><strong>Your whole inventory in the palm of your hand</strong></h1>
                    <p class="lead" style="width:90%;">Stockboy’s intuitive, gesture-based interface makes counting quicker and more accurate—not to mention safer when you’re monkeying around on a ladder counting the top shelf or wrestling in the dark corners of your reach-in.</p>
                </div>
