                    <img src="images/measurescreenshot.png" class="wide">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section style="background:#ecf0f1;position:relative;border-bottom:1px solid #bdc3c7">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="../../images/poscreenshot.png" class="wide">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h1><strong>An orderly way to do your orders</strong></h1>
                    <p class="lead">Stockboy doesn’t just know how much product you have or how much you need, but also where to get more. Stop burning time on the phone, typing emails, navigating vendors’ websites and instead generate purchase orders for each of your vendors in just one click. Just review the order and fire away. Multiple vendors with the same products? Vendors with oddball case breaks or other delivery requirements? Stockboy will sort it out with minimal impact on your budget and your storage.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
